item.title: CVE-2017-20136|2024-08-05T21:45:26.065Z -- itech -- classifieds%20script
item.description: A vulnerability classified as critical has been found in Itech Classifieds Script 7.27. Affected is an unknown function of the file /subpage.php. The manipulation of the argument scat with the input =51' AND 4941=4941 AND 'hoCP'='hoCP leads to sql injection. It is possible to launch the attack remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used.
